### Product Overview

Wow ... this has to be the perfect Anniversary Gift for adventurers and for
those that travel a lot whether it is for work or they are posted abroad.

A fully operational Brass nautical compass, with a unique sundial feature.

**Gift of the Year Award Winner 2015 & 2016**.

## Personalization

The compass lid can be engraved with your own special message of up to 60
characters.

Some ideas are:

  * You will never lose me
  * I won't need this anymore I have found what I was looking for
  * So you can always find your way back to me 
  * Happiness is a direction, not a place
  * Keep this close, listen to your heart and you will never get lost
  * Let's get lost together
  * Let the adventure continue
  * Distance means so little when love means so much
  * xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxox

## Compass Size

Diameter: 7cm

Height 3cm



Please note this gift does take time to make and engrave and will take up to 3
weeks to arrive with you.



    
    
    **Free Shipping on this gift worldwide**
